Britain and Ireland's Next Top Model - Cycle 9, Episode 9




Seven aspiring models remain but there are only six places available on a trip to Barbados next week. Elle Macpherson enrolls them in a Fashion Targets Breast Cancer catwalk event for their biggest showcase yet, and the contestants also take part in a beauty shoot with a cosmetics company.




Original Air Date: 08-Aug-2013
